# pnpm hoisting overrides (pnpm ≥ 10 defaults to strict, non-hoisted node_modules).
# framer-motion v12 re-exports types from motion-dom and motion-utils, but in strict mode
# they are not hoisted into node_modules/, so TypeScript can't resolve the types it needs
# (MotionNodeOptions from motion-dom → the `initial`, `animate`, `whileInView` etc. props).
# Hoisting just these two sub-dependencies fixes the type resolution.
public-hoist-pattern[]=motion-dom
public-hoist-pattern[]=motion-utils
